title: [Gyldemar Forest, Animal Run]
description: Dark oaks crowd together around the thin twisting run, blanketing everything beneath them in dense shadows.  Moss and lichen grow thick on the exposed tree trunks and low-lying foliage of the forest, obscuring details of the immediate surroundings.  A stillness hangs in the heavy damp air.
